Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,亮君跑得好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,加入社团就能改变什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要入部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,肉体改造部的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照了
